Des formations financées à % par le DIF CPF = pas d’avance de COMMENT OUVRIR MON COMPTE FORMATION ? Vous êtes salarié, demandeur d’emploi, non salarié vous bénéficiez d’un droit à la formation que vous pouvez utiliser de manière totalement Première démarche, ouvrir votre compte sur le site du gouvernement en vous dotant de votre numéro de sécurité sociale : 3 minutes suffisent pour ouvrir votre compte et consulter vos droits COMMENT CONSULTER MES DROITS FORMATION ? Pour connaitre le montant de vos droits formation, vous devez vous connecter à votre compte formation depuis le portail web ou l’application mobile Mon compte formation à l’aide votre numéro de sécurité sociale et votre mot de passe QUEL EST LE MONTANT DE MES DROITS FORMATION ? Vos droits dépendent du nombre d’années d’activité professionnelle depuis le 1 er janvier Vos droits sont automatiquement mis à jour sur votre compte en ligne auquel vous pouvez ajouter manuellement votre capital d’heures DIF (heures antérieures à janvier ). Il s’agit de l’ancien nom du dispositif permettant de capitaliser un droit individuel à la Au Décembre , votre employeur a dû vous délivrer, sur Janvier ,une attestation mentionnant votre capital d’heures Si vous avez travaillé en , les droits formation correspondants apparaîtront sur votre compte entre le avril et le juin en fonction de votre Tout au long de votre vie active jusqu’à votre départ à la retraite, votre compteur est alimenté au titre d’une activité professionnelle (en euros) ou une activité d’agent public (en heures). ENCORE UTILISER MES DROITS DIF ? Nod to Our Past The Taste of Today Arak is the staple liqueur of cultures throughout the Eastern Distilled from grapes that are indigenous to the region and flavored with aniseed, the popular drink has a distinct but subtle licorice The high alcohol content in some varieties, combined with the characteristic white color the liqueur turns when diluted with water (just the simple science of emulsion when the aniseed essential oil combines with water!), is how the drink earned its nickname: “The Milk of ” Cultures throughout the region covet the formulas for traditional arak, many preferring to distill their own arak at home over commercial At Miami Arak, we bring those timeless formulas to our distillery where we still make Original What sets our arak apart from others is our collection of 5 flavors — Bubble Gum, Espresso, Lychee, Lemon Lime, and Toasted Marshmallow — that elevate the beverage and give it a distinctive Miami From dinner parties to night clubs, and every occasion in between, arak has been bringing people together for Today, we’ve kept the traditional formula alive and added dimension, depth, and diversity to the original anise liqueur flavor Toast to good vibes & happiness! Connect with Us! © GRAPL   Graph Based Queries | Grapl GRAPL Home Features Contact Blog More GRAPH BASED QUERIES Because attackers think in graphs , Grapl provides a query interface for building out attack Grapl makes it simple to analyze and express complex behaviors with a simple, powerful language - The combination of graph queries and Python means unlimited power for expressing attacker ​ As an example, we can describe a ‘ dropper ’ . Droppers are small malicious programs whose job is to bootstrap the true malicious They are an extremely common tool for attackers, but can be difficult to detect in standard systems due to how many distinct behaviors they With Grapl it’s simple to express the fundamental behavior of a dropper, and start tracking any “dropper-like” programs using the following query: ​ In just a few lines of code we’ve described a complex, attacker With graph based querying, Grapl can catch even the most complex attacks with just a few lines of Get Started Subscribe to our Newsletter! This allows users to tap into the massive Python library and tooling ecosystem and follow standard engineering best Whether it’s unit testing i n CI CD, linting your code for common mistakes or anti patterns, or even applying static analysis tools t o weed out bugs, Python’s ecosystem has you Here you can see mypy , a static type system for Python, finding an error with this query before it’s run, speeding up our iteration cycle and reducing bugs that make it to ​ By allowing you to follow best practices for code maintenance, Grapl drastically reduces maintenance burdens and increases confidence in your ability to detect an Get Started Subscribe to our Newsletter! Connect with Us! © GRAPL   Automated Correlation | Grapl GRAPL Home Features Contact Blog More AUTOMATED CORRELATION Most systems in the past have focused on binary “Good" or “Bad" determinations with an alert based system on top of This approach forces detection engineers to spend all of their time maintaining whitelists, because the cost of a signature matching benign behavior can be Grapl throws this binary model Instead, it provides a gradient risk based system, with automated correlation to build up risk By providing a concept of risk detection engineers can focus on modeling attacker behavior, rather than modeling every single possible user behavior - rather that constantly maintaining whitelists, or disabling alerts altogether, you can simply adjust your risk Every analyzer in Grapl has an associated risk Grapl will automatically correlate the outputs of individual analyzers together to create a composite risk score for the asset, user, or any other specified correlation Here we can see the composite risk where our correlation point is a user’s desktop is involved in two distinct analyzers, Suspicious svchost and Rare Parent of , and so its risk score is significantly higher than just the discrete risks of those two ​ ​ By increasing risk based on overlapping analyzer outputs Grapl’s correlation will quickly lift up particularly suspicious behaviors, and benign, user behaviors will fade into the This means no more wasted time triaging endless false positives, no more maintaining massive whitelists, and more time to fo

In the years since its official beginning, CMS has expanded in size and capability to become an internationally recognized leader in ocean science and graduate We have faculty, ~100 graduate students, and about technical and administrative CMS researchers secure ~$15M in annual research With the vision of a unified global, natural system in mind, the College seeks to build interdisciplinary research teams in collaboration with our local, national, and international CMS scientists work in every ocean on issues of global and regional relevance, with research strengths, including sustainable fisheries, red tides, coral reef health, sea level rise, coastal flooding, ocean acidification, trace metals in seawater, paleoclimate, seafloor mapping, and sensor The work we do at the College of Marine Science is more relevant than Over the last year, the use of the word “Unprecedented” in the news is itself “Unprecedented” Unprecedented floods, hurricanes, and Unprecedented atmospheric temperatures – of the warmest years in the instrumental record since the late have occurred in the period from to Unprecedented ocean temperatures – The ocean heat content has increased at all depths since the and surface waters have warmed by about ° per century globally since Unprecedented atmospheric CO 2 concentrations greater than ppm, which has caused the ocean to become % more To address the importance of the ocean as the major driver in the weather – climate system, CMS researchers use satellites, in situ measurements and models to study where heat is stored in the ocean, how it is transported from the surface ocean to deeper layers, the processes driving these changes, and the chemical and physical In , we witnessed an unprecedented environmental disaster – the Deepwater Horizon oil disaster in the Gulf of The College of Marine Science at the University of South Florida continues to play a major role in understanding the dynamics of petroleum and the ecosystem impacts of the disaster through our international consortium funded by the Gulf of Mexico Research Our graduate program emphasizes student success and career Our educational opportunities span the core disciplines of biology, chemical, geological, and physical oceanography, as well as marine resource Our endowment of $18 million funds fellowships averaging from $9,000 to $22 We have been successful Natural Language Processing for voice and speech — Free registration Features Voice commands Typing with Voice Available languages Browser comptability Natural Language Processing Integrations WordPress plugin Google Analytics Design themes Custom design Pricing Documentation Blog Log in Natural Language Processing NLP module for voice searches and commands We are happy to announce the features of our NLP module (Natural Language Processing), which will help you better understand your customers wants and But what is NLP in general? Natural Language Processing, usually shortened as NLP, is a branch of artificial intelligence that deals with computers and humans using the natural NLP s ultimate objective is to read, decipher, understand, and make sense of the human languages in a valuable Our NLP techniques rely on machine learning to derive meaning from human languages such as sentiment analysis and part of speech How to use NLP module in Voxpow When you created a tracker and users perform some voice searches and commands, you can see them in your dashboard (may vary depends on your settings). After that, we perform a background task to identify the specific sentiment and perform detailed text analysis of each That could need a short amount of time, but in general, you should see your analyzed results a few seconds after we receive them in our The main useful features are to detect: sentiment analysis of your customers - are they are saying something joyful or not part of speech tagging - distinguish verb, adjectives, nouns, As a website owner - it will be an additional source of knowledge and will help you for sure to understand what customers Languages supported in NLP module You need to be aware that we are supporting a limited amount of languages for the NLP That list will be extending with the time, but for now, we support: English German Spanish Italian Portuguese French Japanese Korean Arabic Chinese (Simplified and Traditional). Please keep in mind that those limitations are only in the NLP module, global language support list you can found here . If your tracker uses some of the languages above, you will see the button to the "Text Analysis" After receiving some voice searches and commands from the users, you will notice that some analysis pieces start to show you in the NLP You can check the sentiment analysis field, which is assigned to each specific user There are four options, which are : MIXED POSITIVE NEGATIVE To see the full power of natural language processing, you should take a look at longer phrases, as sometimes, it is challenging to extract sentiment from one world (but is also possible). The first rule in statistics is that data is essential in an aggregated You will probably want to take a look at aggregated stats from your users and find out if they are happy, angry, or have a neutral It is easy to achieve that in aggregated NLP stats, which you can find in your tracker detail page if the tracker s language is available for More about NLP module Voxpow uses the NLP module in the The module makes it easy for our advanced system to easily hear speech, analyze it, and convert it into readable The aim is to speed up the process of Natural language processing is essential as it resolves a wide range of ambiguities in At the same time, it supports useful data structures for applications, like text analytics and voice That’s why Voxpow is increasingly proving itself as the best tool The NLP module allows Voxpow to become the number tool for Companies can use the tool to get insights from their Similarly, the voice to speech technology by Voxpow improves productivity, produces efficiency, and yields a higher return on investment (ROI). Unlike other tools, Voxpow offers data analytics, which is a great way to analyze data through the voice to text It is, likewise, a more sophisticated way to introduce NLP in your business Voxpow uses advanced NLP, which improves contextual understanding of the The software does it through numbers and vectors that represent So, instead of just comprehending the voice as words, the NLP system incorporated in Voxpow enables it to understand similar words and phrases fast and Important pages Blog Documentation FAQ Affiliate program Terms of Service Privacy notice Roadmap & Changelog Company & Mission Videos Contact us Features Voice commands Available languages Browser comptability themes NLP Troubleshoot Google Analytics WordPress plugin Custom design conversion Articles Eight online too… , Facial recogniti… 3, What do online u… , TOP strategic… 1, Newsletter Get a monthly digest of great content We ll never share your email address © Voxpow, Speech Recognition for your ✨System Version —   Register — Free registration Features Voice commands Typing with Voice Available languages Browser comptability Natural Language Processing Integrations WordPress plugin Google Analytics Design themes Custom design Pricing Documentation Blog Log in Create account now Password

3 Key CTA Types For Your Cold Emails Meet Humaily How it works Knowledge base Contacts 3 Key CTA Types For Your Cold Emails CTA (call-to-action) is the final component of your It helps you set the right direction for your It directly influences how your intentions will be perceived by a person on another It literally either kicks you ahead or pushes Before choosing the best CTA, think about this: You already put great effort into writing a perfect email, so what do you expect to happen after your prospect reads it? Based on the outcome, CTAs can fall into one of 3 groups: CTAs According to the analysis of ,174 emails conducted by Gong Labs, an CTA is the most effective Time is the biggest asset for your Instead of asking your prospects for a call, it makes perfect sense to validate their interest in conversation Here are a couple of good examples: - Are you interested in learning more about it? - How do you like the idea to learn more? - Open to learning more? Discovery questions This type of CTA can be a great way to show your curiosity and learn more about their internal processes, company, Using such an approach, you eliminate the pressure on the prospect who hears from you for the first You explore and seek valuable insights that will help you understand if the conversation makes sense in the Some of the examples you can use: - What kind of automation have you incorporated into your outbound services? - What is the #1 thing that helps your team effectively connect with such HR teams? - What outreach channels do you find most effective to initiate the discussion with prospects? - How do you invest in maximizing partner relations? - Does this align with your current objectives or what would you consider as your main sales priority for this year? - Could your team make use of an animated video for communicating your message? Direct meeting requests One of the most frequently included CTAs which over time has become much Prospecting evolves and the human part of it becomes more and more Asking for a meeting in your first message may be a pretty controversial At first glance, it may demonstrate your serious On the other hand, why would your prospect invest his time right away if you have 0 relationships in the past? This will not only be shot in the darkness, but it can also push your prospect Examples: - Are you available for a quick mins discovery call next week? - Can we schedule a call on Tuesday to talk through applying these strategies for your team? - When are you available to have a chat? - Can we jump on a quick chat to see if we can help each other in any way? Just hit us up:) From the heart of the USA & Ukraine Facebook Twitter LinkedIn © All Right Privacy policy   How To Personalize Emails Using 5 Different Data Triggers Meet Humaily How it works Knowledge base Contacts How To Personalize Emails Using 5 Different Data Triggers Why personalization has created so much buzz in the sales world? Times have supply became infinite and buyers have plenty of choices which makes them much more Communication channels have become diversified and easily accessible, so did the technology we use as As a result, buyers are literally overwhelmed with the number of messages and calls they receive every single Personalization came to the rescue when we started to feel that the old approach to starting conversations online no longer Personalization became a solution that addresses a STRONG need to go the extra mile to grab the attention of our To show them that we know with whom and what we re talking To prove that we understand their challenges (or at least trying to gain a better understanding). To let them be participants of the conversation, not victims of another sales And the last and most important — to make them feel Everyone likes Talking to sales professionals and leaders, I noticed a huge shift of perspective from copy paste to a personalized Quality over quantity approach as we like to call That s why I decided to create a handy and brief resource for sales professionals who are on the path of embodying For those willing to experiment with different data triggers to initiate a meaningful Considering all the available data about your prospect and her company, I ended up diving it into 5 different groups: Let s go through each of them to learn how they can help you start more all examples did not include calls to The idea was to show how you can personalize your opening line and naturally align it with your value personalization What data to look for: content, consumed content, content that highlights your prospect, for example:"15 Top Sales Influencers to Follow in " Content is the new gold of According to Omnicore s statistics, 3 million LinkedIn users share content on a weekly Imagine how many people consume this content every single There is a high chance that your prospect is part of either one or both groups — active content producers or active content In any case, content acts as an effective touch

Donate – The Playing Field Project Home Donate Apply Learn About Contact Donate to THE PROJECT Many BIPOC students are marginalized before their first semester of law The immense financial burden of applying to law school (including application fees, application assistance, and costly LSAT prep courses), eliminates BIPOC students from the applicant All donations made via PayPal NEARLY HALF OF BLACK APPLICANTS AREN’T ACCEPTED INTO A SINGLE LAW That’s not a That is an alarming disparity between those who have the opportunity to enter the legal profession, and those who does Until every student — irrespective of race or income status — has a fair shot at law school, this country will never have a representative group of lawyers, lawmakers, and other legal THE BROKEN PIPELINE HOW BARRIERS PREVENT BIPOC FROM ENTERING THE LEGAL FIELD SCHOLARSHIPS Students with the highest LSAT scores are 6 times more likely to receive a Given the high price point of LSAT , a student’s wealth and background often plays into their score, thereby keeping them out of law Your donation provides the LSAT prep courses necessary for our project participants to receive those MENTORS & ADVISORS Students who have access to advisors are more likely to gain acceptance to law It’s not uncommon for an undergraduate school to have a single law school advisor for the entire student Therefore, students are forced to turn to the private sector for advising, a cost many BIPOC students cannot Your donation provides participants access to private, personalized STUDENT LOAN DEBT % of Black and % of Latino students rely on student loans in law BIPOC are funneled into law school with significant economic burdens, which can affect their performance during and after law Your donation alleviates some of these burdens by providing them with the tools they need to be HOW CAN YOU LEVEL THE PLAYING FIELD? A diverse law school student body leads to: A more diverse pool of barred Which leads to more representative policy makers, fighting for sustainable policy Which leads to more people of color serving as judges, upholding a more equitable justice THIS COUNTRY WILL NEVER KNOW EQUALITY UNTIL IT SEES A DIVERSE POOL OF THIS PROCESS DOESN’T BEGIN WITH HIRING MORE DIVERSE LAWYERS — IT STARTS FURTHER BACK, BY FUNNELING MORE BIPOC STUDENTS INTO LAW Join our EMAIL LIST indicates required Email Address First Name Last Name I m interested in being Applicant Donor Volunteer Other The Playing Field Project Foundation works to eliminate the socioeconomic barriers to the legal The Project provides financial assistance to BIPOC for LSAT prep services, law school application assistance, and school prep Quick Links Donate Apply Resources Contact Subscribe The Playing Field Project All Rights   Wayback Machine We will keep fighting for all libraries - stand with us! About Schedule FAQ Our Sponsors Welcome to Hack Frost NL ! Hack Frost NL is the first tech hackathon organized by students from Memorial University of Hack Frost NL invites students of all experience levels to participate in an exciting weekend where you can learn new skills, work on unique projects, and connect with the Hack Frost NL will provide you with the workshops, mentorship, and software your team will need in order to build a successful We will connect you with our sponsors to offer you the opportunity to chat with people in the Our theme for this year will be Data We promise to bring you an unforgettable and fun weekend that cannot be missed! More info coming Stay Frosty! Schedule Note: Event Schedule coming soon! Frequently Asked Questions Am I eligible to participate? Anyone is eligible to participate as a hacker whether you are a high school student, a college or university student, or a recent graduate within the last If you are a professional, there are opportunities for mentors and Everyone is welcome! How much does it cost to participate in Hack Frost NL? Hack Frost NL will be FREE for all I don’t have a strong coding experience, can I still participate? Yes you can! We will run workshops throughout the event that will teach you essential skills, and we will make a dedicated prize category for hackers provided they present a working prototype :) What are the prizes? Our team is currently looking for cool prizes that will offer winners valuable Do I need a team? We think there is nothing better than working in a team, right? We strongly encourage you to form a team of up to 4 Team formation will happen at the If you don’t have a team arranged before the event, we will be hosting a session at the beginning of the Otherwise, you can totally fly solo if you prefer! Will there be swag and merchandise? Yes, our team is working hard to bring you cool swag that will get you right in the hacker We will be updating the website Our Sponsors Interested in sponsoring us? Documentation Contact Log In Get Started for Free Learn what makes Reach℠ work Documentation Overview How Reach℠ Works Reach℠ is a remote support application for IoT By leveraging a mobile device as a bridge between a customer’s IoT device and a support technician, the support technician can directly and securely interact with the customer’s Reach℠ runs on both the customer’s mobile app and the support technician’s The support technician’s computer communicates with the customer’s mobile app, and the mobile app communicates with the IoT device via any communication protocol that the device supports (BLE, MQTT, HTTPS, ). This enables the support technician to control the device’s software in , allowing them to diagnose and fix any issues with the A customer requests a support session using their mobile app, and calls or chats with a customer support representative to initiate the Reach℠ support The support technician provides the customer with a unique pin to type into their mobile app, which acts as a security layer to prevent unauthorized access to the customer’s Once the technician is allowed access, a communication channel is created between the technician and the The technician leverages the Reach℠ communication functionality to get and set information on the device, without the need for customer The customer can sit back and relax while the technician works, without the typical that is often required to identify the technical details that are affecting the customer’s Instead, the technician has access to all of the technical details of the device via the and communication Device Support Reach℠ can support any device that can accept incoming communications of some Common communication protocols include Bluetooth, Bluetooth Low Energy, and local WiFi, but a mobile app with Reach℠ may be customized for any kind of Reach℠ does not support devices that are unable to connect to a different device or to the Reach℠ also doesn’t support existing IoT devices that are unable to accept incoming communications of any form (i.e. no HTTP, no MQTT, no BLE, ). However, if the existing device has the ability to update its firmware and or software, it is likely that an update can enable the device to work with Reach℠. The Reach℠ SDKs are provided in TypeScript JavaScript, Kotlin, and Swift and can be integrated into your device interaction Secure Reach℠ maintains device security by encrypting all network traffic between Technicians can only gain access to the device via the customer’s express permission in the form of the customer entering in a pin that is unique to the remote support session requested by the If the customer’s mobile app connects to their device in the form of Bluetooth, this security is maintained by Reach℠ because all communication to the device continues to occur over the Bluetooth Seamless Customer Interaction Reach℠ is designed to interact seamlessly with a mobile or web app’s UI elements can react to changes in both the device’s connection status and the device’
